{"tid":1516360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文長] 九月撐住，睇下點贏","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:44:30.000Z","uid":74296,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"716eb94ad76c7bd51ddded17d476591a0a939b51","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"本身應該早兩日po，但呢幾日冇乜上連登。上返黎先發現打完自己save咗做draft。<br />\n====================<br />\n<br />\nG7聲明提及香港，好多人都冇諗到。<br />\n有講過話峰會期間會傾香港，但估唔到會將香港擺落聲明入面。<br />\n19年呢份同往年比係短好多，表示各國之間傾得埋既野唔多。但問題係，呢份聲明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港有份</span></span><br />\n即係話，香港問題，係少數佢地有共識既問題。<br />\n<br />\nok，咁佢地有咩人先？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">美、加、英、法、德、意、日、歐</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇錯，G7有八個</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地有無為香港發聲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美：唔講喇，Sir this way！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加：自己有出過聲話關注局勢，有同侵侵傾過密偈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英：有關注，近期對中態度一洗奶袋底頹風，見少少強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法：冇，馬克龍：wfc，反而係黃背心好關注我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n德：昔日我地口中既左膠大國，卻第一個跳出黎出聲，收留咗黃台仰同李東昇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意：印象中冇，最有機會反對G7聲明講香港（孔特係想join一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但佢偏偏早幾日辭咗職，冇政治能量跳出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日：似乎冇，但我地回一回帶：作為G20東道主，同習敗敗會談主動提香港，口交部完全冇符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐：德國呢件事係咩態度基本塞返落歐洲就係咩態度，仲有香港人鏈connect波羅的海三國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSo，份聲明講乜？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>&quot;The G7 reaffirms the existence and importance of the Sino-British Joint Declaration of 1984 on Hong Kong and calls for violence to be avoided.&quot;</em></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞乜呀？你講呢啲？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>reaffirm: confirm the <span style=\"color: red;\">validity</span> of (something previously established)</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>reaffirms the existence and importance</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>有效，存在，重要</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>calls for violence to be avoided</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>say no to 六四2.0</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3fc8754750ca0bde3b6d9b4857bf5f5c9dd39469","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"講就係咁講，但大家都知地獄鬼國冇野做唔出。<br />\n緊急法正在上路，深圳堆係度褶被果班越近10.1就越有可能出。<br />\n我地冇野輸，最多攬炒，但有機會贏，我地都想贏。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點樣贏？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 話俾人地知我地好慘，But how?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1.1 使用外國社交媒體(Facebook以外)</span><br />\nTwitter, Reddit, <span style=\"color: red;\">每個巴絲都一定要有</span>。<br />\n至於點去用(Retweet, Hashtag果類)有其他post，呢度就唔多講喇。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1.2 報．真．料</span><br />\n唔好玩fake news，認真。<br />\n大部分事情既事實幾乎100%有利我方，再加上我地係受害者，搞fake news根本冇好處。<br />\n正如各位巴絲都有提及，CNN已經奶咗一次野，再亂煲fake news係我地自己硬食。<br />\n只要係作既，就總會有穿煲位。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1.3 中国威脅論，赤納粹</span><br />\n智慧燈柱？No，<span style=\"color: red;\">it's FACIAL RECOGNITION TOWER</span>.<br />\nChinazi，唔係我地作，地獄鬼國做緊既野根本同納粹一樣。<br />\n既然係外國眼中我地已經係半個西柏林，我地要做既就係提高chinazi呢隻字既exposure，<br />\nSocial Media用，街頭塗鴉用，被採訪時用，民間記者會睇得到呢篇野既話，都試下講。"},{"pid":"6f88a520499d4fb4c5b1607df2f1be551889770b","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 強調香港既價值</span><br />\n呢樣應該係民間外交應該多提既野。<br />\n香港喺經濟上既價值唔需要我係呢度再講。<br />\n可能呢句話唔係太岩聽，但我地對於世界政治既重要性，在於<span style=\"color: red;\">我地係中国大陸上唯一一個持西方意識型態既地方</span>。<br />\n而且呢幾個月顯示出我地唔止係堅定，<span style=\"color: gold;\">係好撚堅信普世價值：自由、民主、人權</span>。<br />\n一個咁渴望真正民主降臨既地方，你西方世界到宜家仲只係出口術，由得佢被極權吞噬，咁從此喺世界上其他既政治事務，你地都冇名義再發聲。<br />\n<br />\n你地西方想中国民主化？<br />\n相信西方價值既香港，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢既存在到底係有利定不利</span>？<br />\n陸路接壤既香港唔同台灣，佢冇得隨便封關，咁交流就無法禁絕。<br />\n自大講句，我地一定係superior，只要我地保持到不被同化，你支那人黎十個我當你聽得入一個，長久係咪一撚定反cup大陸？<br />\n我地二十幾年黎既問題咪就係，我地有同化部分新移民，但同我地被同化相比，實在太少。<br />\n你出力撐香港，贏咗我地攞雙普選，入境審批權，佢雜種係咪瀨屎都唔掂？<br />\n<br />\n你地西方唔認為中国會走向民主化？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你係咪想極權大數據監控呢套組合spread去所有威權統治既國家</span>？<br />\n仲唔快手清除中国喺國際事務既話語權？<br />\n香港一班外國國籍持有人你貿然接返去對成個國家既人口結構，就業，福利，都會造成大衝擊。如果你食唔落呢班人，你就由佢地留喺香港睇住佢地死？<br />\n<br />\nin all circumstances, 都應該認真出手幫香港，香港同烏克蘭呢類國家既存在係話返畀全世界人聽，西方呢套價值觀，係人所嚮往！一個有完全民主政制既香港，一定係對西方有利！"},{"pid":"4ffa1f3004445ac2da878980cd661e272ab74fc6","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 狂煲中英聯合聲明失效</span><br />\n外國唯一對香港提供援助既正當切入點，只有呢一份文件。<br />\n香港政策法，取消，係懲罰。<br />\n香港人權法，制裁，係懲罰。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假如外國真係要插手，一定係大家一齊跳出黎話中英聯合聲明失效</span>。<br />\n只有咁樣，插手強行逼支那放手畀真普選，甚至獨立，BNO平權，美國第51州，北京條約南京條約恢復行使等等宜家睇落天方夜譚既講法<span style=\"color: gold;\">先有機會變真</span>。<br />\n我地唔怕攬炒，但有得贏，why not？"},{"pid":"5da3378a86ec21fb3a3003147e00563d1fdb84d4","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 白色恐怖</span><br />\n請開始<span style=\"color: red;\">逆向批鬥</span>。<br />\n佢藍屍係點篤我地灰？cap我地圖去支共網upload（唔太清楚呢項，請補充）<br />\nreport畀老闆，client知。<br />\n我地要做既野好簡單，藍屍有我地friend時，我地都有佢地friend (除非你set privacy做everyone喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我地確定一個人係藍，就攞佢相開新ac（個email address要同佢有關，例如佢既英文名，生日年份），作返佢地支持抗爭既po，然後篤佢地灰。<br />\n呢樣係冇得validate，因為fb, ig, twitter唔係支那既platform，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢會盲信收到既資料</span>，跟返呢d途徑報串，佢地一定奶屎。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果發大咗開始唔信，就可以保護到某d被cap圖既自己人</span>。"},{"pid":"e8d4a1e426511cba4dd42ae632331c792dbe561e","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">5. 因應近日泛民被批評既睇法</span><br />\n我唔贊成去指責泛民點點點，我只想大家思考一樣野：<br />\n7.1手足夾走白頭佬，其實係代表<span style=\"color: red;\">我地已經不再信任當下既代議政制</span>，<br />\n往後我地所做既決定，基本上都係直接民主，我地每人都只代表我地自己。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你議員喺前線用你地既身分幫我地，無任歡迎</span>。<br />\n但我地既意見，由於你地既past record，都係我地自己講就得喇。<br />\n冇屈你，咁你地真係出賣過我地好多次。<br />\n<br />\n宜家我地要做既係，去英美議員Twitter留返我地既意見(集中Retweet一個comment)，<span style=\"color: red;\">每一次comment都要寫返佢地唔代表我地</span>。<br />\n有咩好處呢？<br />\n如果泛民同外國議員傾既野同我地comment既野一致，咁泛民係重申返我地想要既野。<br />\n如果係唔同既，我地推到個comment上去畀佢睇到，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢會知泛民唔係represent我地，泛民既意見唔係香港人既意見</span>。<br />\n<br />\n九月一定係更加黑暗既一個月，支那為咗洗十月太平地係乜撚都做得出，但我地每擋住一招，就更加接近勝利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐住，真係有得贏！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb58a81d9be6356ff60094d340a8692922d61a4","tid":1516360,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pt2YGgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpt2YGgQ.jpg&h=e3955959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1515063/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1515063/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a918625f093ef13738affeb7f264b0d596cb9586","tid":1516360,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n孫子兵法：求其上，得其中；求其中，得其下；求其下，必敗。<br />\n上：中共<br />\n中：林鄭<br />\n下：警犬"},{"pid":"78f6b907309bccb1b4e762eaede40112583f7948","tid":1516360,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8c39b9e7100dc8ed8ddaf80223057801d438516","tid":1516360,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbnrz0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbnrz0.gif&h=dd99b35f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95979c197849ad36b181dc4818a96db67b1f8de2","tid":1516360,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"推你"},{"pid":"2d4ef8f9b49c3662f3a4ed93e7b55e1fd7d363b1","tid":1516360,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a553c3d39ff1e52b3914f141ed0ae6ae86dcdb9b","tid":1516360,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"邊有得唔推"},{"pid":"64c7fb4c6e5db3b62be16aa4a9f77b074a84fcb6","tid":1516360,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95d613e866109c8a5d9e299f53063b608760881","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"推  (1/10) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5624fb7aaea302bdc9043d479ff1a0a711bbd8e","tid":1516360,"uid":50692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b7806653998717fcaf3d60da20b072423194aa1","tid":1516360,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b22b6a7856fd9b0e6badd63e3e3caa2a693abd2","tid":1516360,"uid":74296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:28:30.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推呢個<br />\n<br />\n[文長] 九月撐住，睇下點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516416</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e36d18a5fa9f1cdce279ee0af406367914d9e527","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"},{"pid":"4a8dcec9b139dd41d1db768535a7bc53a5585389","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"},{"pid":"0105ceb498438cb4043e468fcc9bb63dcbb8ce5d","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"},{"pid":"0cbbb4f8b5295292305525b04de4de5736e145e2","tid":1516360,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"過埋後日先算，後日手足要小心呀"},{"pid":"94feaa65098e8f4484cbf350d4a80e4523c82437","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"},{"pid":"f77855c000282615f06f8269ed41de93d4aca7bc","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"},{"pid":"0a7eb634331fe8ca0825ae41ac3d0964f824589a","tid":1516360,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"榮耀歸於香港<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄"}]}